window.bookSummaryJSON = "Frank Muller was one of the most talented narrators to ever record a book. As Stephen King said, \"[When Frank reads], the blind will see, the lame will walk, and the deaf will hear.\"<p>Enjoy this montage of selections from some of Frank's recordings.</p>"; 
